      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "- **Start With One Goal**\n   - Don’t try to be perfect at everything at once  \n   - Start with: “This game, I’m focusing on not wasting mats”  \n   - Or: “This game, I’m working on mid-game rotates”  \n -  **Lock In – This Takes Time**\n  - Building that in-game confidence comes from hundreds of reps\n  - You can’t skip this phase — everyone has to go through it  \n  - But the more focused your reps are, the faster you’ll improve\n-    **Videos to watch**\n  - <https://youtu.be/V4n2uvb0Ziw?si=ekKKmxC3MKpClxh2>\n  - <https://youtu.be/4QEQgLrfiFk?si=c6aU0Wx9Ox_KvW0X>\n  - <https://youtu.be/ubom606WcQY?si=dyv7q1ftikbStfQz>\n  - <https://youtu.be/tdZqne5ZF-g?t=348>\n  - <https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e4U3Rntg96o>\n-# credit to @Pyrox @Deleted User for making this guide",
